                <span class="section-eyebrow">System Design</span>
                <h2>SDI for Corn: Key Design Parameters</h2>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <li>Lateral spacing: 30 or 60 inches (matching row spacing)</li>
                    <li>Installation depth: 12–16 inches below the surface</li>
                    <li>Emitter spacing: 8–16 inches depending on soil texture</li>
                    <li>System designed for 10–15% peak ET replacement per day</li>
                    <li>Fertilizer injection compatible with UAN, 10-34-0, and AMS</li>
                    <li>Pressure regulation at 10–12 PSI for flat-field corn</li>
                    <li>Filters: 120-mesh disc or sand media + secondary screen</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:28px;display:inline-block;">Find a Dealer</a>
